trans-unit.source: Provides constants for compatibility with the Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Show" name="Show" href=""></xref> method.
trans-unit.target: Gir konstanter for kompatibilitet med Visual Basic 6.0 <xref uid="langword_csharp_Show" name="Show" href=""> </xref> metoden.

trans-unit.source: In Visual Basic 6.0, the `Modal` parameter of the `Show` method was used to determine whether a form would be shown as a modal dialog box.
trans-unit.target: I Visual Basic 6.0 den `Modal` -parameteren for den `Show` metoden ble brukt til å finne ut om en form skal vises som en modal dialogboks.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], the `Modal` parameter is replaced by two different Show methods: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.ShowDialog%2A>.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], `Modal` parameteren erstattes med to metoder Vis: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.ShowDialog%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.ShowDialog%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A>

trans-unit.source: These constants enable code that has been upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0 to continue to run without additional modification.
trans-unit.target: Disse konstantene Aktiver kode som har blitt oppgradert fra Visual Basic 6.0 skal fortsette å kjøre uten ekstra endring.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Functions and objects in the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6> namespace are provided for use by the tools for upgrading from Visual Basic 6.0 to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Funksjoner og objekter i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>navneområde er angitt for bruk av verktøyene for oppgradering fra Visual Basic 6.0 til [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)].</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6>

trans-unit.source: In most cases, these functions and objects duplicate functionality that you can find in other namespaces in the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: I de fleste tilfeller disse funksjonene og objekter duplisert funksjonaliteten som du finner andre navneområder i den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: They are necessary only when the Visual Basic 6.0 code model differs significantly from the [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementation.
trans-unit.target: De er nødvendige bare når Visual Basic 6.0 kode modellen er ulikt betydelig den [!INCLUDE[dnprdnshort](~/add/includes/dnprdnshort-md.md)] implementeringen.

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbModal" name="vbModal" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Tilsvarer Visual Basic 6.0 konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbModal" name="vbModal" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Equivalent to the Visual Basic 6.0 constant <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbModeless" name="vbModeless" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Tilsvarer Visual Basic 6.0 konstanten <xref uid="langword_csharp_vbModeless" name="vbModeless" href=""> </xref>.
